<item>
            <title>[DERBY-3227] Remove final from all getConnection() methods in EmbeddedDataSource</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3227</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The final modifier makes it impossible to wrap Derby connections in P6Spy, for example.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The network ClientDataSource doesn&apos;t use final, either.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch: Replace &quot;public final Connection&quot; with &quot;public Connection&quot; two times.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
